///Position;
static, relative, fixed and absolute:

    static: default position, normal natural flow;

    relative: nudge the default position a few pixels and use the left, top, bottom and right commands

    Absolute: absolutely removed from the normal flow and placed near the latest coontainer

    fixed: Stuck to the same position in the page


/// Collapsing Margins:

don't use margin bottom with margin top with following divs
define everything in one margin direction (bottom for example)
